  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK555">
<l>allaṟpaṭ ṭāṟṟā taḻutakaṇ ṇīraṉṟē </l>
<l> celvattait tēykkum paṭai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Will not the tears, shed by a people who cannot endure the oppression which they suffer (from their king), become a saw to waste away his wealth ?</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
